    format("What's that? You don't want to…\p If you want to see how skilled I am, you come see me anytime!")
}

text BattleFrontier_Lounge7_Text_RightTutorIntro {
    format("Ihihihi!\p I know it's hard to see now, but I used to be one fantastic TRAINER.\p I had a reputation as the most invincible SWIMMER around, I tell you!\p … … … … … …\p What's wrong? You don't believe me.\p I'm not like that buffoonish woman over there. I'm actually experienced!\p I can prove it to you. I can teach your POKéMON hard and\l yet pretty moves.\p But my lessons don't come free. How about paying for the moves I teach\l with a wee bit of Battle Points?")
}

