text BattleFrontier_Lounge7_Text_ThinkLadiesDontGetAlong {
    format("Those ladies, the way they bad-mouth each other, you probably think that\l they don't get along.\p But if that were true, they wouldn't stay out here together, would they?")
}

text BattleFrontier_Lounge7_Text_LadiesWereStrongAndBeautiful {
    format("When I was just a wee YOUNGSTER, those ladies were strong and beautiful.\p They were idols among us TRAINERS.\p Even now, age hasn't dulled their abilities.\p In fact, their POKéMON moves have grown even more polished.\p But… For some reason, I can't help but feel this…\p Time is so cruel…")
}

